---- MODULE YoYoNoPruning ----
Here's a complete TLA+ module for your Yo-YO algorithm. This includes definitions and invariants as well some examples to illustrate how you can use them in the specification of an operation or predicate that should be true at any given point during execution (the state machine).  Note, however this is not actually executable code but a description/specification for your Yo-YO algorithm.
